  "remarks": "Pars Special Economic Energy Zone (PSEEZ) is a subsidiary (100 %) of the State-owned National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC). The National Iranian Oil Company (NIOC) is a State-owned and operated entity providing substantial financial resources and support to the Government of Iran. Furthermore, PSEEZ’s Assaluyeh Port provides port operating services to IRISL.",
